### NOTA: El controlador necesita actualizarse para usar 'interes_anual' en lugar de 'tope_reintegro'
### El sanitizer actual espera 'tope_reintegro' pero la entidad tiene 'interes_anual'

### Get all wallets
GET http://localhost:3000/api/wallets

### Create a wallet (usando campos del sanitizer actual)
# @name createWallet
POST http://localhost:3000/api/wallets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "MercadoPago",
  "discount": "20%",
  "fechaDesde": "2025-01-01",
  "fechaHasta": "2025-12-31",
  "category": "fintech",
  "availableDays": [1,2,3,4,5,6],
  "discountType": "reintegro",
  "tope_reintegro": 12,
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/mercadopago.png"
}

### Capture wallet id
@walletId = {{createWallet.response.body.data.id}}

### Get one wallet
GET http://localhost:3000/api/wallets/{{walletId}}

### Update wallet
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/wallets/{{walletId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "MercadoPago Premium",
  "discount": "25%",
  "tope_reintegro": 15,
  "category": "premium-fintech",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/mercadopago-premium.png"
}

